### List GitHub Repositories
GET https://api.github.com/user/repos
Authorization: token {{$dotenv GITHUB_TOKEN}}
Accept: application/vnd.github.v3+json

### List GitHub Repositories (with pagination - first 30 repos)
GET https://api.github.com/user/repos?per_page=30&page=1
Authorization: token YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/vnd.github.v3+json

### List GitHub Repositories (only public repos)
GET https://api.github.com/user/repos?visibility=public
Authorization: token YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/vnd.github.v3+json

### List GitHub Repositories (only private repos)
GET https://api.github.com/user/repos?visibility=private
Authorization: token YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/vnd.github.v3+json

### List GitHub Repositories (sorted by creation date, newest first)
GET https://api.github.com/user/repos?sort=created&direction=desc
Authorization: token YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/vnd.github.v3+json
